    <title>Functional Accessibility Evaluator (FAE) 2.0</title>
    <contents>
      <ul>
        <li>Designed for:
          <ul>
            <li>Managers</li>
            <li>Web designers</li>
            <li>Software developers</li>
            <li>Quality assurance testers</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Website rule result summaries and implementation status</li>
